parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Spark Plug Failure and Cylinder Head Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of spark plugs can cause damage to the cylinder head threads, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing engine failure, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Coolant leaking into the cylinder can cause engine knocking, misfiring, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure Leading to Vehicle Fires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause vehicles to catch fire, even when turned off and parked, resulting in total loss of the vehicle, potential injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: often in the engine compartment or wheel wells
with no warning signs or symptoms.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Corrosion and Strap Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the fuel tank and failure of the fuel tank straps can cause gasoline to leak, leading to a fire hazard, and potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Gasoline leaking from the fuel tank
broken or corroded fuel tank straps

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Inspection and Repair under Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to properly inspect and repair the fuel tank and its components during a recall can lead to continued safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: Lack of notification about fuel tank corrosion or damage during recall repair
inadequate repair or replacement of fuel tank components
continued fuel leaks or other safety issues after recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank mounting can cause the fuel tank to detach from the vehicle, leading to fuel leaks, fires, and accidents, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The fuel tank detaches from the vehicle
a quarter of a tank of fuel spills
the fuel tank is loose or hanging from the vehicle.
